Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,02
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:02.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.38,0:02:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看不到人的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.17,0:02:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听不到声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再也…见不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.43,0:02:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是「不在」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.52,0:02:29.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咲良不在 卫不在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.53,0:02:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士不在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.15,0:02:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道生不在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.86,0:02:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多很多人都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.97,0:02:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 都不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.46,0:02:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 我却还在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:02:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.93,0:03:04.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑和真矢都想战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.09,0:03:06.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.49,0:03:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北极…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:14.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是可能有去无回的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.26,0:03:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也再没有其他选择了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泥土
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.17,0:03:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和祝福者的身体一样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.17,0:03:36.51,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(520,80)}Festum
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.23,0:03:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把大家 把总士…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.42,0:03:45.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夺走的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:50.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.39,0:03:53.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.02,0:03:57.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还…从来没见过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:01.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然会碰我的工具
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.46,0:04:09.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…你不是在Alvis吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.70,0:04:11.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来拿换洗的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.62,0:04:15.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有…来看看你的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.37,0:04:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 我的身体 还能动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在变得和咲良一样之前 我还有时间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.94,0:04:35.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.60,0:04:41.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑 法芙娜你已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:46.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士说了 我们可能要参加人类军的作战行动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.46,0:04:47.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们做的用来打倒祝福者的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:57.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能已经超乎你们的想像 成为了我们的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说傻话 所以就要让我批准你们参加人类军鲁莽的决战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 只有这个办法了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.31,0:05:07.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.26,0:05:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸你自己失去妈妈的时候肯定也是这样的心情吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:14.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 你没有打倒敌人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.52,0:05:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我有！有法芙娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.16,0:05:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你错了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.16,0:05:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:23.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我养大就是为了对付他们的吧！爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住嘴！不许再说这种话！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.95,0:05:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说 如果把你和Mk.Sein投入决战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.07,0:05:32.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么保护岛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.99,0:05:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有远见和卡农
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.09,0:05:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还有剑司
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.97,0:05:40.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们…会保护岛的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.49,0:05:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你凭什么保证连逃离前线的人都会再开法芙娜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑司还剩下什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咲良和卫都不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.63,0:05:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连他妈妈也不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:53.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在他还有什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.67,0:05:55.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过不了多久他就会自己提出要开了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.38,0:05:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么…蠢话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.97,0:06:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己也明白的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.08,0:06:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该明白吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.18,0:06:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我去啊 爸爸！求你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.63,0:06:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁我现在还动得了 趁我还没变成咲良那样！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.21,0:06:11.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一个人去北极
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.16,0:06:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.65,0:06:17.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身体越来越迟钝了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.03,0:06:19.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛也很快要看不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.76,0:06:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会变得什么也想不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.91,0:06:28.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很快就会…活着变成另一种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:31.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就要不在了啊 爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:37.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远见医生很快就会找到救你们的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.65,0:06:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.30,0:06:39.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么来得及！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.31,0:06:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了 爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.81,0:06:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁我还是我的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我去战斗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了 让我去啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.61,0:06:56.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我一个人去啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.94,0:06:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:06.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是决定岛要怎样作战的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸你是现在这个岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.77,0:07:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一一个会命令我们去战斗的人！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.59,0:07:21.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吗…爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.00,0:07:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会送走你们 送走所有想要战斗的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.34,0:07:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.46,0:07:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等到岛的复原工作结束
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.10,0:07:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后 我会准备送你去北极
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把手上的泥巴洗干净
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:15.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等干掉 就弄不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.17,0:08:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好寂寞的风
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到最近 整个岛上还都开满了花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.19,0:08:47.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在树 花和虫子却都死了 只剩下寂静的风
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.13,0:08:53.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的浪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:58.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为岛缺了一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.95,0:09:06.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整个岛的周围都是那么大的浪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是唯独我的身边 却是毫无起伏的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.05,0:09:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要开上法芙娜 悲伤和寂寞的感觉都会从心里消失
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.61,0:09:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子离开的时候 是不是也是这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.13,0:09:40.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为太想消除悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.49,0:09:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我竟然这么想开法芙娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:54.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:58.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不在了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和祝福者有什么区别呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…和祝福者有什么区别呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家里一团乱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.36,0:10:31.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的家 我的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:41.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厨房 客厅 餐桌 浴室
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.84,0:10:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都像是陌生的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:54.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈的房间 工作的用品全都掉在地上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:11:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈要是看到了会生气的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:07.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和平的地方 安全又温暖的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.84,0:11:15.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到头来 这才是我最珍惜的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 它们全都失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.96,0:11:27.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 卫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咲良 陪着我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.41,0:11:43.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来个人 陪着我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 已经没有任何地方待得下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:12:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子 还是第一次那样求我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从他很小的时候开始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就从来没有那样过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.99,0:12:23.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把他送到去了就回不来的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.02,0:12:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除此之外 我就没有其他办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.94,0:12:32.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红音…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,03
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.35,0:12:43.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家寻求着希望 却走向与之不同的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.97,0:12:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的答案 才刚刚觉醒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.55,0:12:55.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点 快来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.68,0:12:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回到岛上来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.69,0:13:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则会就这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.78,0:13:10.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡农 对不起 我来迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.69,0:13:14.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 该道歉的是我 要你陪我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说要想驾驶神剑型 就要和别人一起训练
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:23.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:29.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为了解彼此的心 对于驾驶我们的法芙娜是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:33.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽佐间老师在做准备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.16,0:13:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进去了之后要去找到对方 这个你有听说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:46.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 虽然不知道要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.33,0:13:48.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我会试试的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.75,0:13:51.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会想办法去找你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.84,0:13:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然没变
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:23.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全是一团迷雾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.41,0:14:26.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人也看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.73,0:14:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平稳的水面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.52,0:14:35.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它的那一边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.53,0:14:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,映着我的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.74,0:14:48.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 还映着很多其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.69,0:14:58.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一骑 卡农 近藤 还有大家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.94,0:15:01.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子也在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.37,0:15:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日井 咲良 还有小楯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.20,0:15:18.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岛上的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.43,0:15:25.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 姐姐 道生哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.25,0:15:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边有爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.97,0:15:39.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像都在镜子的里面一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.35,0:15:46.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像在外面的我才是被关起来的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:52.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.77,0:15:56.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面…有光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.69,0:16:05.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火 像手掌那么大的火
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.74,0:16:10.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燃烧着 落了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:20.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红得刺眼 又漂亮的火
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事 火往雾的那边去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在叫我过去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑暗的海
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:55.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我站在沉了一半的船上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.17,0:17:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲜红的木材造出的老旧的船
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.32,0:17:11.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船头亮着光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.00,0:17:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.82,0:17:22.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴比伦 我那已经不动的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.20,0:17:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这艘船吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正乘着坏掉的船 在黑暗的海上徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.08,0:17:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.88,0:17:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是让人生厌的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.36,0:17:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些 会被真矢看到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.03,0:18:02.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海的上面出现了火
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:12.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里也有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.96,0:18:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一大团红色的火…越变越大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.31,0:18:29.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里的火…有一团靠过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.12,0:18:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.74,0:18:48.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.12,0:19:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…这团火是…道生…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.49,0:19:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雾渐渐散了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.19,0:19:15.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有船
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.69,0:19:21.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真壮观…好多的火
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.29,0:19:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你吗 道生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.04,0:19:42.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.14,0:19:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算爬上来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.85,0:19:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真 真矢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.89,0:19:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 卡农你果然在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.91,0:19:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成你…你爬上来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.72,0:20:02.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 因为到处都是洞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.95,0:20:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就觉得可能爬得上来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.04,0:20:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡农？你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.38,0:20:11.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:20.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好多火
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:23.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是雅各布之火
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.93,0:20:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣经里提到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.69,0:20:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死者的灵魂会变成火 引导在夜海中彷徨的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死去的人们的…火
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.62,0:20:46.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像盂兰盆会的灯笼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.71,0:20:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 火往海里漂过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.61,0:20:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那团火把我带到这里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.71,0:21:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来…那是…一个人的灵魂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.24,0:21:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.53,0:21:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道为什么 我就是知道那是翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.87,0:21:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说 她明明只是个素未谋面的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.77,0:21:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是翔子把你带到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…翔子吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:36.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要走了吗 道生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.37,0:21:40.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道生…哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.16,0:21:46.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和其他的火一起 往海那边去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.59,0:21:52.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道每一团火都是谁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.59,0:21:56.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我全都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.72,0:22:00.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.82,0:22:04.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些是战死的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.02,0:22:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边是我已经毁灭的故乡的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.80,0:22:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 船前头的火呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.21,0:22:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是谁的？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.47,0:22:22.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…是我的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.79,0:22:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想让人看到这么荒凉的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.56,0:22:38.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 卡农你…很温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.37,0:22:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.19,0:22:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直都记得 那些死去的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.31,0:22:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你才能够不迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.84,0:22:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些日子里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.87,0:23:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人死去是家常便饭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.10,0:23:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我努力说服自己不去在意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.77,0:23:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人会死 自己会死
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.13,0:23:13.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些事都不去在意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.57,0:23:18.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 大家都活着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.02,0:23:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活在我的心里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.34,0:23:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.76,0:23:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的海
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.92,0:23:37.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是笼罩在一团雾里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.61,0:23:44.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 大家都在水的那一边…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.23,0:23:48.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水的…那一边？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.88,0:23:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里有一片风平浪静的地方对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.91,0:24:03.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所在的地方 一直都是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.31,0:24:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有起伏
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.03,0:24:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.67,0:24:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.81,0:24:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在笑着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.40,0:24:19.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是…你的心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.88,0:24:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.98,0:24:26.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被雾笼罩的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.60,0:24:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会是因为想要保护在那里的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.91,0:24:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雾在…保护…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.36,0:24:39.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.90,0:24:42.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雾之所以迷惑人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.62,0:24:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为要保护雾里的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.43,0:24:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是…这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.94,0:24:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.77,0:25:03.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.97,0:25:06.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.30,0:25:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些我都是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.84,0:25:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真矢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.98,0:25:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡农 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.93,0:25:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝福者没有 而我们有的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.42,0:25:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.50,0:25:28.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是为了确认这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.77,0:25:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才想要来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.44,0:25:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来到 我自己的心里
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,04
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.18,0:26:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是近藤家
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.12,0:26:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要老师
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.79,0:26:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.35,0:26:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是到处都找不到我妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.75,0:26:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里 要老师明明也为了咲良的事那么操劳了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.34,0:26:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去Alvis…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.23,0:26:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会 我…没事
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.61,0:26:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这里…是我家
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.17,0:26:58.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.31,0:27:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要一直待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.35,0:27:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为妈妈可能会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.09,0:27:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我没去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.82,0:27:45.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑司
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.26,0:27:46.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.91,0:27:49.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是有几句话要跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.08,0:27:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡农…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.80,0:28:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前都没觉得奇怪过
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.69,0:28:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到我居然只能这样死死抓着
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.95,0:28:34.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来这么爬着山 就能觉得像是在爸爸背上一样
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.52,0:28:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种不拼命撑着身体就可能会掉下去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.76,0:28:44.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.79,0:28:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.61,0:29:03.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 已经不在了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.66,0:29:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远见
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.42,0:29:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住我
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.05,0:29:12.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.03,0:29:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不行的 你身体都那样了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.09,0:29:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.38,0:29:27.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远见…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.19,0:29:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 最后一点我想自己爬上来
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.33,0:29:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最…后？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.62,0:29:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.93,0:29:56.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.19,0:30:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你是来对我发火的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.61,0:30:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.38,0:30:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是来嘲笑我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.04,0:30:23.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.03,0:30:29.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妈妈的事…真的很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.06,0:30:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.88,0:30:38.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得我在想 她说不定会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.42,0:30:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑司…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.86,0:30:46.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明得保护妈妈才行的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.36,0:30:53.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…妈妈…却说要保护我…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.69,0:31:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的妈妈…也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.42,0:31:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她为了保护我而死了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.64,0:31:15.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要跟我说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.85,0:31:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你的机体…给我
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.12,0:31:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有战斗的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.07,0:31:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会驾驶好的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.30,0:31:32.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…让给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.05,0:31:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我的Mk.Ⅷ？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.97,0:31:40.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会替你一起战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.42,0:31:44.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就留在这里 保护自己的家
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.20,0:31:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的家…我的家么？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.04,0:31:56.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑司…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.90,0:31:59.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看了还不明白吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.88,0:32:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的东西都一团乱！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.77,0:32:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才不是我的家！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.00,0:32:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 你为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.45,0:32:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…我不知道啊 谁会知道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.89,0:32:20.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑司…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.61,0:32:30.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我没资格说这些话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.75,0:32:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该保护这里的 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.53,0:32:43.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.17,0:32:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有其他法芙娜的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.69,0:32:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在战斗中的位置和我相同
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.32,0:32:56.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记录了和我相似的心的机体会比较易于一体化
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.69,0:33:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相似…？我和你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.07,0:33:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.98,0:33:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你没有异议 我就去向司令申请变更机体
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.03,0:33:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢着 哪里像了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.11,0:33:13.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你比我…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.34,0:33:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都想要待在浮在海上的安全的东西上
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.08,0:33:21.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说海…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.33,0:33:25.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞑想训练时的海
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.13,0:33:29.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看过了你们过去的记录
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.23,0:33:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他人都是什么东西也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.79,0:33:37.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你创造出了自己的容身之地
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.14,0:33:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我则是船
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.50,0:33:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.39,0:33:52.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去开…那部机体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.10,0:33:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你一时回答不了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.79,0:34:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就等到确定了我的适应性之后再来
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.11,0:34:05.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是完全不一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.35,0:34:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.77,0:34:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船是会动的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.23,0:34:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚礁…是不会想要移动的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.28,0:34:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.02,0:34:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个地方比我的船美丽多了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.02,0:34:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想看到那幅心灵风景在战斗中变得荒凉
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.58,0:34:33.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是为了咲良
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.93,0:34:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的…心
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.34,0:34:51.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.77,0:35:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种东西 早就变成这样了！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,05
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.42,0:35:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有失去
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.33,0:35:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还有一些留下的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.38,0:35:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案已经渐渐接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.67,0:35:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.77,0:35:25.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快一点 快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.14,0:35:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.14,0:35:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要犹豫 过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.17,0:35:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要迷失 来到这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.17,0:35:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.58,0:35:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想见的人 都在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.25,0:35:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有留下任何东西
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.64,0:35:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是对自己 还是对岛来说
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.25,0:36:04.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么活下来的人是自己
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.30,0:36:09.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想破了脑袋也找不到答案
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.24,0:36:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去的自己全都逐渐分崩离析 消失不见
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.75,0:36:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该选择的不是是否要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.92,0:36:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是要以怎样的心去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.52,0:36:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除此之外 没有第二条道路
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.46,0:36:32.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那时 在那个人出现之前
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.86,0:36:37.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警报
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.21,0:36:38.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.11,0:36:41.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决意要走
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.74,0:36:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个人都下定了决心
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.79,0:36:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这时 那个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.88,0:36:56.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.67,0:37:00.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久之前 曾一度失去的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.99,0:37:05.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在宏大的奔流中反复诞生的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.59,0:37:10.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案从遥远的过去开始
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.13,0:37:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,历经漫长的岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.28,0:37:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到了龙宫岛
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.01,0:37:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们 又不是我们的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.80,0:37:23.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他们 又不是他们的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.17,0:37:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与我和龙宫岛的内核成对的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.38,0:37:34.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真壁红音意志的继承者
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.40,0:37:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这最后关头
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.16,0:37:38.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指明了最后的去向
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.24,0:37:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望——连接我们与他们的最后的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.96,0:37:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我选择拥有「我」这颗心的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.28,0:37:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案已经昭示
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.61,0:38:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我活在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.80,0:38:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我确实存在于这里的最后的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.32,0:38:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.81,0:38:18.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甲洋走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.75,0:38:23.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们…会保护岛
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.68,0:38:26.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.94,0:38:27.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.29,0:38:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你要上哪去
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.32,0:38:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去找爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.94,0:38:40.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认祝福者消失了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.94,0:38:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城乙姬一醒就叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.90,0:38:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重新展开伪装镜面
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.62,0:38:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让岛以现有速度前进
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.38,0:38:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧分析新获得的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.60,0:38:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.22,0:38:57.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.97,0:39:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.74,0:39:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.78,0:39:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是红音
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.06,0:39:10.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的妈妈…已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.97,0:39:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.29,0:39:16.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 她的心现在也还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.75,0:39:19.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与她希望沟通的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.41,0:39:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有我们一起活着
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.88,0:39:24.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是这样而已
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.29,0:39:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.62,0:39:28.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么简单的事
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.66,0:39:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我却直到这一刻才发现
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.46,0:39:34.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.38,0:39:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.27,0:39:41.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在Alvis里待命
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.87,0:39:44.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远见医生现在正在分析医学资料
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.34,0:39:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她应该会需要你们的身体数据
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.02,0:39:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了拯救你们
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.54,0:39:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.45,0:39:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.19,0:39:57.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.46,0:40:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.93,0:40:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑 你说过
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.69,0:40:11.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我失去你妈妈时的心情也和你一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.51,0:40:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.05,0:40:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在可以熟练运用的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.19,0:40:19.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那时确实都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.44,0:40:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说消灭敌人了 就连能抵抗得像样点的武器都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.67,0:40:26.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.17,0:40:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.62,0:40:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可有现在的你所没有的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.53,0:40:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妈妈把他托付给了我
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.76,0:40:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是指…？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.81,0:40:43.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主要资料的分析一旦有了头绪 就要立即开会
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.56,0:40:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去通知大家 他们也要出席
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.32,0:40:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.28,0:40:58.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有你 一骑
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,06
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.22,0:41:05.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.15,0:41:10.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑 驾驶员要到医务室集合
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.96,0:41:13.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是需要我们现在的数据
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.98,0:41:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.03,0:41:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你走着难受 不如我背你？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.30,0:41:17.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.99,0:41:22.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都在等我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.70,0:41:24.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁让我们是一伙的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.10,0:41:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要我们丢下你的话就直说
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.72,0:41:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.77,0:41:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 叔叔他怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.47,0:41:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该很震惊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.34,0:41:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出了那种事 那个…你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.63,0:41:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妈妈已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.80,0:41:47.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.96,0:41:50.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 她的心还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.73,0:41:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是 以后也是
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.71,0:41:58.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸和我都是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.61,0:42:01.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.10,0:42:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.37,0:42:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.14,0:42:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.48,0:42:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妈妈说她会安排一下
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.50,0:42:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们能在她确认数据的时候去吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.10,0:42:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢天谢地
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.44,0:42:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我一直没吃什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.97,0:42:17.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.86,0:42:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？心不在焉的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.18,0:42:21.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.44,0:42:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑 要怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.46,0:42:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.10,0:42:28.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.63,0:42:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.79,0:42:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会和大家一起去的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.72,0:42:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以确定的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.79,0:42:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这并非一切的终结
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.15,0:42:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在前路茫茫的不安之中
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.35,0:42:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在丧失许多人的痛苦之中
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.84,0:43:02.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望也一定会继续存在下去
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.79,0:43:06.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一心一意地相信着
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.23,0:43:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信一定有些东西是永恒的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.87,0:43:20.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信无论何时都一定能找到它
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.60,0:43:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信即使会无数次将它迷失
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.05,0:43:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也一定能再度寻回
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.52,0:43:33.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们始终相信
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.22,0:43:40.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就意味着我们现在存在于这里
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.76,0:43:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那里吗
